{"tid":1910992,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【ICAC訓緊覺？】CSI口罩疑通街賣    申訴署查懲教物流署生產分發安排","createTime":"2020-03-05T04:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T23:18:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1220bb51fc6f5d57d6af83663edd1997490ac347","tid":1910992,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Kz1DMHdoEBWnvOSSAuQ4oQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-03/4815a410-5e94-11ea-b6d7-988eb0501273\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKz1DMHdoEBWnvOSSAuQ4oQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-03%2F4815a410-5e94-11ea-b6d7-988eb0501273&h=b0c4cfe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情造成全城出現「口罩荒」，而坊間卻出現大量由懲教署生產的口罩(即俗稱的CSI口罩)，懷疑有人非法出售CSI口罩。申訴專員趙慧賢今日(5日)宣布展開主動調查，審研有關懲教署生產的口罩在生產、分發和點存方面的安排。<br />\n<br />\n趙表示，CSI口罩主要供應給政府物流服務署，並由物流署分發給各有需要的政府部門使用，鑑於近月武漢肺炎疫情，市民對口罩需求急增，留意到不少傳媒和市民指出有CSI口罩流出市面，令人質疑有人涉嫌挪用或轉售CSI口罩，因此申訴專員決定向懲教署及物流署展開主動調查，審研兩部門在規管CSI口罩的生產、分發和點存方面的機制、程序和執行情況。<br />\n<br />\n趙又指，根據政府發布的資料，CSI口罩主要是供應給各政府部門作日常及應變計劃之用。懲教署去年每月平均向物流署供應110萬個口罩，並將小部分口罩出售予社福機構、學校等非政府組織。由於近日有報道指CSI口罩流出市面，社會關注CSI口罩有可能被濫用，而申訴專員公署亦收到有關投訴，故決定展開調查，審研懲教署及物流署有否不妥善之處。<br />\n<br />\n她續指，若發現有關機制或程序存在不足，會向相關部門提出改善建議，以望能從源頭堵截漏洞，避免出現CSI口罩被濫用的情況。申訴專員現邀請市民於4月6日或之前，以書面方式就上述課題向申訴專員公署提供相關資料或意見。"},{"pid":"e80c1db4fcecc8e12fce9b6c22a79b9e0ef054f1","tid":1910992,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"明顯係1989年支那式貪污「倒賣」 (叫「官倒」)<br />\n<br />\n由官方渠道低價取得的物資, 高價倒賣民間獲利<br />\n<br />\nICAC竟然係訓覺<br />\n<br />\n由無牙老虎去搞「改善建議」？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f726756ef9b1b703bcfb39834e3054ee7053b21","tid":1910992,"uid":2924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:55:28.000Z","msg":"ICAC 根本係笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390c2e58121991747aa7929dee7eb5c21d96ccfb","tid":1910992,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"冇可疑"},{"pid":"d460c9005ae5b3ee2c1609fd2a9b878e76b0f59d","tid":1910992,"uid":292816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"390c2e58121991747aa7929dee7eb5c21d96ccfb","tid":1910992,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"冇可疑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"趙慧賢係昔日狗房二當家<br />\n你唔係覺得會有野呀"},{"pid":"cc413e55f20b865c3cb49485586e4c5c7370aee1","tid":1910992,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"盒裝，紀律部隊用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔駛查，查唔到"},{"pid":"66cf4a023fc5959a4ce489de92cd4f6ffd89f582","tid":1910992,"uid":59327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289cedb196cadcc992a7b3d485fc591b68a02e82","tid":1910992,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:06:32.000Z","msg":"申訴專員公署好似都係一樣冇實權"},{"pid":"c955588ba808b5bf7c8b560dad2480770778030c","tid":1910992,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dac13e246f1bdb7d519b7c31ea1c9317c0e2d31","tid":1910992,"uid":67353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:18:23.000Z","msg":"唔好再遲d先查 諗住d人用得7788先查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets